ctrl + f4 --> file close
alt + f4 --> window close
f11 --> full screen toggle
ctrl + tab --> switch among recent files [History].

ctrl + c [with empty selection] --> line copy
ctrl + x [with empty selection] --> line cut

alt + up/down arrow --> line move
shift+alt + up/down arrow --> line copy
ctrl + up/down arrow --> line scroll

ctrl + ` --> toggle integrated terminal.

ctrl + p -- filename --> file search
shift + ctrl + p --> command pallete

ctrl + p -- @symbolname --> symbol search (like variable name / keywords / identifiers)

ctrl + p -- #symbolname --> search all symbols.

f8 shift+f8 -- goto errors.            


ctrl + k m --> change language

alt + shift + a --> block comment
ctrl + / --> line comment

ctrl+b --> toggle side bar
